# ğŸš€ Kubernetes Master Node Cluster Setup on Ubuntu 24.04

This guide explains â€” step by step â€” how to install and configure a **Kubernetes v1.32** single-node (master) cluster using **containerd** and **Calico CNI**.  

Each command is explained with its **purpose** and **technical reasoning**, so you not only *run* it but also *understand* it.

